               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Taʾammǝra ʾIyasus “Miracles of Jesus” (fols. 1ra-8va), fragment
                     I-1) ʾƎsaggǝd la-malakotǝka… “I worship Thy Godhead…” (fols. 2ra-4va l. 16)
                     (cp. ChRep no. 335), incomplete.
 II-2) Taʾammǝra ʾIyasus “Miracles of
                     Jesus”: 2 miracles, not numbered (fols. 4va l. 16-7vb), fols. misplaced,
                     incomplete.</summary>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">

                     <incipit>
                        <foreign xml:lang="en"/>
                     </incipit>
                     <explicit>
                        <foreign xml:lang="en"/>
                     </explicit>
                     <note/>
                  </msItem>
               </msContents>
