                        <collation>Two bifolia (fols. 3-4 and fols. 5-6) have
                                 been inserted between fols. 2v and 7r.
 A bifolio (fols. 1 and
                                 8) originally belonging to Ms. MM-006 has been used as
                                 protection.
                        </collation>
                        <condition key="deficient">The boards are missing. ff. are misplaced, most
                           of the leaves are missing. The sewing is destroyed.
 The Ms. is badly
                           stained with water. Text on fols 1r-v and 8r-v is barely legible.
 A
                           bifolio (fols. 1 and 8) which was used as protection originates from a
                           different codex (MM-006).</condition>
